title: Oklahoma State officially opens new residential complex (Oklahoma State University)
text: ( Source : Oklahoma State University ) Oklahoma State University held a grand opening and ribbon cutting for the university's latest residential life facility following the OSU /A&M Board of Regents regularly scheduled meeting in Stillwater
